reviewText: I loved these two movies! I used to own then, but I loaned them out and never got them back :(  Where can I find them to buy again???

This is a very funny video made by some missionaries on their preperation day.  Very shore - 15- 20 minutes I think.

I would guess that this is an accidental pricing.  I'd love to buy it, but only for $5.99.  If you have a copy and would like to sell it, email me at tuckerrd@ldsces.org
